Template: wire-sysio/install-service
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Register the wire-sysio-nodeop systemd service?
 Registers the packaged wire-sysio-nodeop unit with systemd and creates the
 service directories (/etc/wire/sysio, /var/lib/wire/sysio/data,
 /var/log/wire/sysio).
 .
 If you decline, the unit file remains available under
 /usr/lib/systemd/system but nothing is registered or created.

Template: wire-sysio/enable-service
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Enable and start wire-sysio-nodeop?
 Adds wire-sysio-nodeop to the default boot target and starts it
 immediately (systemctl enable --now).
 .
 If you decline, the service is registered but neither enabled at boot
 nor started.
